{"tid":1326104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【精彩】今日午飯，隔離枱逆權對話","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:38:10.000Z","uid":216978,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd1b63da7bec4419d0ae2154d72852326c39310","tid":1326104,"uid":216978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"今日午飯好精彩！隔離枱3位約50歲西裝呀叔(A,B,C)對話：<br />\n<br />\nA: 所以咪唔應該俾班警察入去囉，冇事發生喎冇偷嘢冇火足，商場又冇報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nB: 但係班人叫囂搞亂唒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA: 喂！我講下野，冇打人打爛野冇偷野架喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nB: 商場都話冇報警啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有條友忍唔住：而家就係有片影住商場兩位保安帶成班警察入去呀嘛！<br />\n<br />\n地契只係合約條款，唔能夠凌駕法律。就算地契許可警察進出，商場都有權以保障公民權利既法律拒絕警察擅闖私人產業。<br />\n<br />\n記者唔暴力喇掛？點解警察唔俾記者拍攝，又打記者？就係唔想你地影到警察濫捕濫打！警察係人民僕人，警權唔可以無限大<br />\n<br />\nB (沉默)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nC (頭頭是道地 up 頭)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果條友對面既西裝友突然瞪眼拍手👏🏻👏🏻：呢啲掌聲係我送俾你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果條友：多謝！見到香港而家咁樣真係好嬲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉向 B 講：而家香港庫房俾政府搶唒啲錢，根本官迫民反，你睇下沙中線？偷工減料，起完、拆完、再起，無人需要問責！你唔發聲即係揾自己笨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後女侍應為果條友執餐時：你頭先 ... (微笑) 嘻嘻...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ed57d67c26a71427c8e2fd6dba7848335e0a16","tid":1326104,"uid":210140,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"女侍應有冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d0e9ca19dcadb29aa528de0df1bbcea0de9c89","tid":1326104,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdpBE6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdpBE6K.png&h=2510ef0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddc87ec8265ef9be9437c7de323ec615b516a87e","tid":1326104,"uid":216978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27ed57d67c26a71427c8e2fd6dba7848335e0a16","tid":1326104,"uid":210140,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"女侍應有冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8c7e612160238e86916e29e1d7521e55769e57","tid":1326104,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc87ec8265ef9be9437c7de323ec615b516a87e","tid":1326104,"uid":216978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27ed57d67c26a71427c8e2fd6dba7848335e0a16","tid":1326104,"uid":210140,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"女侍應有冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"10秒救樓豬老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b20804eb4cd5d195ba988ad79005a89f3f1c35f","tid":1326104,"uid":70439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwRHAQa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwRHAQa.png&h=9d1a6c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"837d09029d225670f4ed785f54fa6ee5c30519f8","tid":1326104,"uid":37757,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"af8c7e612